OL,3,C'Crumbling' Government cyber defences
OL,4,Coutpaced by cyber criminals ` report
OL,6,FGovernment cyber defences have not
OL,7,Fkept up with the dangerous and
OL,8,Fevolving threats from hackers, a
OL,9,Freport from MPs has warned.
OL,11,FThe Public Accounts Committee (PAC)
OL,12,Fsaid hostile states and criminals have
OL,13,Fdeveloped the ability to severely
OL,14,Fdisrupt public services and critical
OL,15,Fnational infrastructure faster than
OL,16,Fthe Government expected.
