OL,7,Fprofile cyber attacks on UK retailers,
OL,8,Fincluding Marks and Spencer and Co-op,
OL,9,Fincidents which Chancellor of the
OL,10,FDuchy of Lancaster Pat McFadden said
OL,11,Fshould be a "wake-up call" for British
OL,12,Fbusinesses, as he announced a new #16
OL,13,Fmillion package to boost cyber
OL,14,Fdefences during a cyber security
OL,15,Fconference earlier this week.
