OL,3,C'Crumbling' Government cyber defences
OL,4,Coutpaced by cyber criminals ` report
OL,6,FIn its report conclusions, the PAC
OL,7,Falso said there was a shortage in
OL,8,FGovernment of technical cyber skills
OL,9,Fand experience, cyber security had not
OL,10,Fbeen prioritised as a key issue, gaps
OL,11,Fremained in the Government's
OL,12,Funderstanding of how resilient public
OL,13,Fsector IT systems were to attack, and
OL,14,Fthat existing supply chains were
OL,15,Fcomplicated to properly secure.
OL,17,FIt called on the Cabinet Office to
OL,18,Fcarry out a major audit of IT systems
OL,19,Fand report back with details on how it
OL,20,Fplans to fix the range of issues
OL,21,Fraised.
