OL,3,C'Crumbling' Government cyber defences
OL,4,Coutpaced by cyber criminals ` report
OL,6,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown, chairman
OL,7,Fof the committee, said: "Government
OL,8,Fdepartments are beginning to wake up
OL,9,Fto the serious cyber threat they face.
OL,11,F"It is positive to see independent
OL,12,Fverification now in place to gain a
OL,13,Fbetter picture on critical systems
OL,14,Fresilience.
OL,16,F"Unfortunately, this has only served
OL,17,Fto confirm that our battlements are
OL,18,Fcrumbling.
