OL,3,C'Crumbling' Government cyber defences
OL,4,Coutpaced by cyber criminals ` report
OL,6,F"A serious cyber attack is not some
OL,7,Fabstract event taking place in the
OL,8,Fdigital sphere.
OL,10,F"The British Library cyber attack is a
OL,11,Fprime example of the long-lasting cost
OL,12,Fand disruption that these events can
OL,13,Fcause.
OL,15,F"Hostile states and criminals have the
OL,16,Fability to do serious and lasting harm
OL,17,Fto our nation and people's lives.
