OL,4,Coutpaced by cyber criminals ` report
OL,6,F"If the Government is to meet its own
OL,7,Fambition to harden resilience in the
OL,8,Fwider public sector, a fundamental
OL,9,Fstep change will be required.
OL,11,F"This will involve infusing every top
OL,12,Fteam with the required digital
OL,13,Fexpertise, with cyber and digital
OL,14,Fspecialists at the top level of every
OL,15,Fdepartment, both management and boards
OL,16,Fto bring about a change in thinking
OL,17,Fthroughout the Civil Service for
OL,18,Fgreater threat awareness and digital
OL,19,Ftransformation.
