OL,6,F"Part of this will be Government
OL,7,Ffinally grasping the nettle on
OL,8,Foffering competitive salaries for
OL,9,Fdigital professionals, and we were
OL,10,Fencouraged to hear the Cabinet Office
OL,11,Fthinking in these terms.
OL,13,F"For too long, Whitehall has been
OL,14,Funwilling to offer attractive
OL,15,Fremuneration for experts who are able
OL,16,Fto secure high-paid work elsewhere.
