OL,4,Coutpaced by cyber criminals ` report
OL,6,F"Making sure that the right people are
OL,7,Fin the right jobs to defend the UK
OL,8,Fagainst this serious threat, and
OL,9,Freducing the use of expensive
OL,10,Fcontractors at the same time, is
OL,11,Fclearly sound value for money.
OL,13,F"This is an issue our committee will
OL,14,Fcontinue to scrutinise closely.
OL,16,F"It must not take a devastating attack
OL,17,Fon a critical piece of the country's
OL,18,Finfrastructure for defensive action to
OL,19,Fbe taken."
